headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Robinhood Markets (HOOD) After Its Recent Share Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Robinhood Markets is still priced attractively after its big run, this article will walk through what the current share price might imply about its value. The stock last closed at US$75.86, with returns of 51.4% over the past year and a very large gain over three years, while also seeing a 26.6% decline over the last month and a 34.2% decline year to date.
